definitions.definition: Referring to products produced from milk .

subdefinitions.definition: Referring to products produced from animal milk as opposed to non-milk substitutes.

definitions.definition: Referring to the milk production and processing industries .
On food labelling, containing fats only from dairy sources (e.g. dairy ice cream ).

main_definition: Referring to products produced from milk .
